---
title: Beef & Mushroom Wellington with Filo Pastry, Mashed Potato, Green Beans & Gravy
description: If you can’t pull together a show-stopping feast at Christmas, when can you? Introducing the star of tonight’s menu, our beef and
mushroom wellington! Wrapped in flaky filo pastry and served with a rich worcestershire gravy, creamy mashed potatoes, and tender steamed asparagus, it’s a festive feast that brings warmth and cheer to your table!

*We’ve replaced the green beans in this recipe with asparagus due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6723830706f5566883435eb9-0168dfa4.jpeg
